1998-12-08 22:11  night

	* AUTHORS: first version.

1998-12-08 17:11  monaka

	* kernel/BTRON/init/libMittenCmd/command.c: Minor change.

1998-12-08 17:10  monaka

	* kernel/BTRON/init/libMitten/: MitnStack.c, builtin.c,
	commands.inc, evaluator.c, math.c, parse.c: Include files changed.

1998-12-08 17:08  monaka

	* kernel/BTRON/init/libMitten/: command.c, command.h: There was
	modified how to search built-in command.  command structure was
	already obsolute.

1998-12-08 14:38  monaka

	* kernel/BTRON/init/: init.h, main.c, lib/atoi.c,
	lib/init-stdlib.h, lib/stdlib.c, libMitten/CellMemory.h,
	libMitten/CellPool.c, libMitten/GarbageCollect.c,
	libMitten/Makefile, libMitten/MitnDict.c, libMitten/MitnStack.c,
	libMitten/builtin.c, libMitten/command.c, libMitten/command.h,
	libMitten/commands.inc, libMitten/evaluator.c, libMitten/math.c,
	libMitten/mitten-command.h, libMitten/parse.c,
	libMittenCmd/command.c, libMittenCmd/graphic.c: I init has been
	included the Mitten Scripting Language since this release.  But,
	it's just a first preview. So you can't use many convenience
	features. Mitten works extension scripting environment like Tcl,
	Guile, Windows Scripting Host, and so on. If you wished, you may
	connect your function written in C to Mitten operator. If you
	wished, you may call Mitten from C.

1998-12-07 23:30  night

	* kernel/BTRON/make/Makefile: 作成するドライバに rs232c を追加。

1998-12-07 23:29  night

	* kernel/BTRON/device/rs232c/rs232c_internal.h: 各シリアルポートの
	ベース I/O アドレスを指定する COMx_BASE マクロを 追加。
	分周レジスタを指定するときに使用する UART_FRE マクロを追加。 マクロ
	UART_IER のコメント変更(割り込みイネーブルレジスタ -> 割り込み
	許可レジスタ)。

1998-12-07 23:21  night

	* kernel/BTRON/device/rs232c/rs232c.h: ボーレート指定用マクロ
	(Bxxxx) の追加。

1998-12-07 23:19  night

	* kernel/BTRON/device/rs232c/rs232c.c: probe_rs232c
	()、setup_rs232c ()、write_byte_rs232c ()、 read_byte_rs232c ()
	の関数の追加。 中身はまだ作っていない。

